==Entering the public domain in countries with life + 50 years== In most countries of Africa and Asia, as well as [[Canada]], [[Belarus]], [[Bolivia]], [[New Zealand]], [[Egypt]] and [[Uruguay]], a work enters the [[public domain]] 50 years after the creator's death.
